}class Notification extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Column(
      children: [
        Container(
          width: 375,
          height: 812,
          clipBehavior: Clip.antiAlias,
          decoration: BoxDecoration(color: Colors.white),
          child: Stack(
            children: [
              Positioned(
                left: 0,
                top: 0,
                child: Container(
                  width: 375,
                  height: 51,
                  decoration: BoxDecoration(color: Colors.white),
                  child: Stack(
                    children: [
                      Positioned(
                        left: 0,
